Name: sugarcane production | sugarcane | EN15804GD, U
Category: A:Agriculture, forestry and fishing/01:Crop and animal production, hunting and related service activities/011:Growing of non-perennial crops/0114:Growing of sugar cane
Description: Cultivation of sugarcane with 89% mechanical harvest and 64% mechanized planting.The percentage of total area are: 18% plant cane (i.e. fist year cane); 72% for ratoon cane (second to fifth year cane) and 10% for reforming (fallow period).
